snippet.title: Wormate.io 1,273,954 SCORE World Biggest Worm in Wormateio Gameplay!
snippet.description:
Wormate.io is a funny and interesting version of the popular Slither.io. Eat candy to grow and become larger you must watch out for the other worms they can kill you 
if your head collide with their tail or body. Move your mouse to control your worm and click it for acceleration.
I hope you guys enjoyed this video. Thanks for all your support!!
Have a nice day and I'll see you guys in the next video!
Subscribe to keep you update with latest video!
